### Create a Device [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer rEWnnWOlGlFc0O6YEixmXsmyIkxblaKUTUnLCj1HAeHpBqVfzEdPUEmkKZMf
    + Attributes (Device Create)

