### Update a Device [PUT /device/{id}]

+ Parameters
    + id: 1 (number, required) - ID of a device.

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer rEWnnWOlGlFc0O6YEixmXsmyIkxblaKUTUnLCj1HAeHpBqVfzEdPUEmkKZMf
    + Attributes (Device Update)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes

        - data (Device Full)

### Delete a Device [DELETE /device/{id}]

+ Parameters
    + id: 2 (number, required) - ID of a device.

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer rEWnnWOlGlFc0O6YEixmXsmyIkxblaKUTUnLCj1HAeHpBqVfzEdPUEmkKZMf

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes

            - data (Device Full)

## Data Structures

### Device Update (object)
- Include Device Create
- mac_address: `DA:A0:FK:2C:1E:74` (string)

### Device Create (object)

- name: `Kitchen` (string) - Name of a device
- mac_address: `DA:A0:ZX:2C:1E:74` (string) - MAC address of a device
- description: `Numquam laboriosam et et consequatur tempora error blanditiis` (string) - Description of a device

### Device Full (object)

- id: `1` (number, required) - ID of a device
- Include Device Create
- created_at: `2016-08-04T11:01:52+0000` (string) - ISO8601 datetime where a device is created
- updated_at: `2016-08-04T11:01:52+0000` (string) - ISO8601 datetime where a device is updated


